# Routes, APIs, Forms Rules

## Routes

- Export `meta` in every page route module.
- Use `withNoAuth` on login page export only; layout handles auth for all other admin pages.
- Use `clientLoader` for data loading on admin pages.
- Export `handle.pageShell` overrides on finance CRUD pages.

## API Objects

- Use `adminApiClient` for all endpoints.
- Define uppercase path constants (e.g., `ADMIN_FINANCE_DAILY_SALES_PATH`).
- Whitelist payload/query fields explicitly.
- Clean filter params with `removeObjectEmptyAttributes`.

## Forms

- Keep domain forms in `app/domains/<domain-model>/*-form.jsx`.
- Keep Zod schemas in matching `*-schema.js` files.
- Use `FormProvider` for nested shared field components.
- Use `getApiErrorToastConfig` and `setApiErrorsToFormFields` in route-level submit handlers.
